        "name": "FDA pump registry observational data collection and comparison",
        "description": "Retrospective observational study using pre-existing FDA generic centrifugal pump registry measurements. No prospective experimental protocol was defined; operating conditions were not controlled by the study team. Data were collected under varying laboratory conditions across multiple sites.",
        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "startedAtTime": "2025-06-01T00:00:00Z",
        "endedAtTime": "2025-11-15T00:00:00Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/cou2-mc-uncertainty",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on hemolysis predictions",
      "description": "Monte Carlo sampling (N=2000) was performed over inlet velocity profiles, blood viscosity, and rotor tip-clearance to propagate parametric uncertainty through the CFD hemolysis model. The resulting 95 % prediction intervals were compared with registry scatter to assess whether model uncertainty bounds are conservative relative to observed variability.",
      "validationMetric": "95-percentile-prediction-interval-coverage",
