    "rationale": "The validation team concluded that the observational-study comparison against the FDA pump registry, combined with Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification, collectively satisfies the evidentiary standard for absolute hemolysis prediction at MRL 5. The breadth of the registry dataset (47 operating points, multi-site, five-year span) was judged to provide robustness equivalent to a prospective controlled experiment. NRMSE of 8.3 % and 91 % prediction-interval coverage were deemed sufficient. All credibility factor gaps were acknowledged but considered acceptable given the totality of evidence. Decision: Accepted.",
